---
import PortfolioLayout from "../layouts/PortfolioLayout.astro";
---

<PortfolioLayout title="AI | Jessie Zhang" description="AI enablement with governance and adoption: MIA and MMM Copilot.">
  <section class="rounded-2xl border bg-neutral-900 p-8 text-white shadow-md">
    <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-white/70">AI Enablement & Automation</div>
    <h1 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight">Governed + adopted AI (not demos)</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 max-w-prose text-sm leading-6 text-white/80">
      I operationalize AI to scale marketing intelligence and measurement adoption with guardrails:
      citations, no-inference rules, and role-/scenario-based experiences.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
      {["Citations", "No inference", "Role-based", "Scenario-based", "Enablement"].map((t) => (
        <span class="rounded-full bg-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wider text-white/80">
          {t}
        </span>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="mia" class="mt-6 rounded-2xl border bg-white p-7 shadow-sm scroll-mt-28">
    <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-neutral-500">Case Study</div>
    <h2 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-neutral-900">MIA — Marketing Intelligence Assistant</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-neutral-700">
      A governed self-serve copilot for marketing SOPs, ownership clarity, and “where the truth lives” across tools—built for Marketing and used by Sales and Product stakeholders.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-50 p-5">
        <h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-neutral-600">Audience</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-neutral-700">Marketing organization + stakeholders in Sales and Product</p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-50 p-5">
        <h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-neutral-600">Sources</h3>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm leading-6 text-neutral-700">
          <li>Static marketing SOPs</li>
          <li>RACI charts</li>
          <li>Index of dashboards and data locations (Salesforce, Tableau, spreadsheets)</li>
          <li>Pre-structured performance data for users without dashboard access</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-50 p-5">
        <h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-neutral-600">Guardrails</h3>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm leading-6 text-neutral-700">
          <li>Source citations</li>
          <li>No inference (answer only from known sources)</li>
          <li>Role-based details</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-50 p-5">
        <h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-neutral-600">Adoption</h3>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm leading-6 text-neutral-700">
          <li>Training</li>
          <li>Ambassador model</li>
          <li>Office hours</li>
          <li>Company-wide newsletter + animated case-study videos</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-4 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-5">
      <h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-neutral-600">Early outcomes (directional)</h3>
      <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm leading-6 text-neutral-700">
        <li>Made it easy to find data locations and indexing information</li>
        <li>Strong use case for new-hire onboarding</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="mmm" class="mt-6 rounded-2xl border bg-white p-7 shadow-sm scroll-mt-28">
    <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-neutral-500">Case Study</div>
    <h2 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-neutral-900">MMM Copilot — Learning + Decision Support</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-neutral-700">
      A role- and scenario-based MMM assistant for channel owners and revenue marketers—designed to accelerate MMM ramp-up and support day-to-day media investment decisions.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-50 p-5">
        <h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-neutral-600">Audience</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-neutral-700">Marketing organization, especially channel owners and revenue marketers</p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-50 p-5">
        <h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-neutral-600">Sources</h3>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm leading-6 text-neutral-700">
          <li>MMM best practices guide</li>
          <li>Role-based workflows</li>
          <li>Scenario cases</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-50 p-5">
        <h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-neutral-600">Guardrails</h3>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm leading-6 text-neutral-700">
          <li>Role-based guidance</li>
          <li>Scenario-based decision workflows</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-50 p-5">
        <h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-neutral-600">Adoption</h3>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm leading-6 text-neutral-700">
          <li>Training</li>
          <li>Learning hub</li>
          <li>Office hours</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-4 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-5">
      <h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-neutral-600">Early outcomes (directional)</h3>
      <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm leading-6 text-neutral-700">
        <li>Marketers ramped MMM knowledge quickly with a 24/7 assistant</li>
        <li>Supported media investment decisions for stakeholders new to MMM</li>
        <li>High engagement from intended audience (~80% usage by target group)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-6 rounded-2xl border bg-white p-7 shadow-sm">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-extrabold tracking-tight text-neutral-900">Next AI directions (portfolio-worthy)</h2>
    <div class="mt-4 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-50 p-5">
        <h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-neutral-600">KPI Trust Copilot</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-neutral-700">
          Detect metric drift, anomalies, freshness issues, and QA gaps before exec readouts.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-50 p-5">
        <h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-neutral-600">MOR Narrative Generator</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-neutral-700">
          Draft “what changed / why / so what / now what” with human approval and edit tracking.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PortfolioLayout>
